--- description: Repos for Neuro-Symbolic AI Toolkit date: dummy content --- import ReposByTag from '../components/ReposByTag.js'; This page lists all the neuro-symbolic AI related repositories being developed at IBM Research. The repositories are categorized in the following six major categories. There are tags beyond these categories too, these tags show the projects/pipelines where the repository was deployed.
1. Logical Neural Network (LNN) 1. Natural language processing via reasoning (NLP) 1. Knowledge foundation (KF) 1. Learning with less (LwL) 1. Knowledge augmented sequential decision making (SDM) 1. Human in the loop (HIL)
